


User Commands                                            BOX2D(1)



NAME
     box2d - filters images using a 2D 3x3 boxcar filter


SYNOPSIS
     box2d input output


DESCRIPTION
     box2d filters images in Analyze format using  a  3x3  boxcar
     filter  in  2  dimensions  only.  The original intent was to
     remove noise from CT images to facilitate segmentation.


EXAMPLE
     box2d p5000ct p5000ct2


